body_html: I ran into this just now, and as a temporary fix (since it's blocking anyone from building the Android demos with the top-of-tree code) I've copied the relevant file to the location it's expected. We should also fix the code, but the simplest fix (adding a prefix to the name) failed because it's used as a file name for the destination of the download.
